		https://social.technet.microsoft.com/Forums/scriptcenter/en-US/ab677f49-97be-4e3b-9021-4a6803e7516f/using-html-application-hta-to-create-a-dynamic-link-to-a-local-file?forum=ITCG
		
		file.name & vbcrlf
		
		-->
</body></html>
